---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SparkleDelight from "../components/SparkleDelight";
---

<Layout title="pybash">
  <main
    class="min-h-screen px-4 py-8 sm:px-8 sm:py-12 md:px-16 md:py-16 lg:px-24"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10">
      <nav class="flex flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <div class="font-sans text-lg sm:text-base">pybash.</div>
        <a
          href="mailto:hi@pybash.xyz?subject=Let's%20Talk"
          class="animate-gradient-shift rounded-full bg-[length:200%_200%] px-3 py-2 font-sans text-base text-white sm:px-4 sm:text-lg"
          >Let's talk &#x2197;</a
        >
      </nav>
      <div
        class="text-2xl font-light leading-tight sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
      >
        Engineer with over half a decade<br />of experience in <span
          class="rounded-lg bg-green-300 px-1 pb-1 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out hover:bg-transparent hover:px-0 hover:text-green-500 sm:px-2"
          >shaping products</span
        ><br />
        that &nbsp;<SparkleDelight client:load />&nbsp; users.
      </div>
      <div class="font-sans text-sm sm:text-base">
        I worked with teams to design experiences that feel effortless,<br
          class="hidden sm:block"
        />and built systems that push ideas into reality.
      </div>
      <div
        class="mt-12 w-fit rounded-full px-3 py-2 font-sans text-base ring-1 ring-black sm:mt-16 sm:px-4 sm:text-lg md:mt-20 lg:mt-24"
      >
        Selected work
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 sm:gap-10 md:gap-14">
        <div>
          <div class="font-italic text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">
            messing around at <span class="text-green-500">grass labs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pb-4 font-ellograph">2024 &rarr; 20▒▒</div>
          <div
            class="min-w-screen -mx-4 divide-y divide-black border border-x-transparent border-y-black px-4 font-ellograph text-lg font-semibold sm:-mx-8 sm:px-8 sm:text-xl md:-mx-16 md:px-16 lg:-mx-24 lg:px-24"
          >
            <a
              href="https://grasslabs.dev"
              class="-mx-4 block py-4 underline underline-offset-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:cursor-external hover:bg-black/10 sm:-mx-8 md:-mx-16 lg:-mx-24"
            >
              <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">puppetmaster</div>
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://dripcraft.xyz"
              class="-mx-4 block py-4 underline underline-offset-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:cursor-external hover:bg-black/10 sm:-mx-8 md:-mx-16 lg:-mx-24"
            >
              <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">dripcraft</div>
            </a>
            <div
              class="group -mx-4 py-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:cursor-custom hover:bg-black/10 sm:-mx-8 md:-mx-16 lg:-mx-24"
            >
              <div
                class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24"
              >
                <span class="underline underline-offset-4">rift</span>
                <span
                  class="font-sans text-sm opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 ease-in-out group-hover:opacity-100"
                >
                  A crypto-first marketplace for the creator economy
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-italic text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">
            engineer at <span class="text-blue-500">10Planet</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pb-4 font-ellograph">2023 &rarr; 2024</div>
          <div
            class="min-w-screen -mx-4 divide-y divide-black border border-x-transparent border-y-black px-4 font-ellograph text-lg font-semibold sm:-mx-8 sm:px-8 sm:text-xl md:-mx-16 md:px-16 lg:-mx-24 lg:px-24"
          >
            <a
              href="https://deva.me"
              class="-mx-4 block py-4 underline underline-offset-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:cursor-external hover:bg-black/10 sm:-mx-8 md:-mx-16 lg:-mx-24"
            >
              <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">deva.me</div>
            </a>
            <div
              class="group -mx-4 py-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:cursor-custom hover:bg-black/10 sm:-mx-8 md:-mx-16 lg:-mx-24"
            >
              <div
                class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24"
              >
                <span class="underline underline-offset-4">genie</span>
                <span
                  class="font-sans text-sm opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 ease-in-out group-hover:opacity-100"
                >
                  Sitewide AI helper for Deva.me
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-italic text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">
            creator of <span class="text-red-500">harvence</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pb-4 font-ellograph">2024 &rarr; 2025</div>
          <div
            class="min-w-screen -mx-4 divide-y divide-black border border-x-transparent border-y-black px-4 font-ellograph text-lg font-semibold underline underline-offset-4 sm:-mx-8 sm:px-8 sm:text-xl md:-mx-16 md:px-16 lg:-mx-24 lg:px-24"
          >
            <a
              href="https://harvence.pybash.xyz"
              class="-mx-4 block py-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:cursor-external hover:bg-black/10 sm:-mx-8 md:-mx-16 lg:-mx-24"
            >
              <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">mobile app</div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-italic text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">
            i <span class="text-amber-500">write</span>
            <span class="text-sm sm:text-base">(sometimes)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pb-4 font-ellograph">2022 &rarr; 20▒▒</div>
          <div
            class="min-w-screen -mx-4 divide-y divide-black border border-x-transparent border-y-black px-4 font-ellograph text-lg font-semibold underline underline-offset-4 sm:-mx-8 sm:px-8 sm:text-xl md:-mx-16 md:px-16 lg:-mx-24 lg:px-24"
          >
            <a
              href="https://journal.pybash.xyz/writing/cursor"
              class="-mx-4 block py-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:cursor-external hover:bg-black/10 sm:-mx-8 md:-mx-16 lg:-mx-24"
            >
              <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">
                giving ai another chance
              </div>
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://journal.pybash.xyz/writing/4s-13ms"
              class="-mx-4 block py-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:cursor-external hover:bg-black/10 sm:-mx-8 md:-mx-16 lg:-mx-24"
            >
              <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">4s &rarr; 13 ms</div>
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://journal.pybash.xyz/writing/turning-the-tables"
              class="-mx-4 block py-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:cursor-external hover:bg-black/10 sm:-mx-8 md:-mx-16 lg:-mx-24"
            >
              <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">
                turning the tables
              </div>
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://journal.pybash.xyz/writing/the-devils-workshop"
              class="-mx-4 block py-4 transition duration-300 ease-in-out hover:cursor-external hover:bg-black/10 sm:-mx-8 md:-mx-16 lg:-mx-24"
            >
              <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24">
                the devil's workshop
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col items-start gap-8 pt-12 sm:gap-12 sm:pt-16 md:gap-24 md:pt-20 lg:flex-row lg:gap-36"
        >
          <div class="font-italic text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl">
            history
          </div>
          <div
            class="columns-1 gap-6 text-justify font-sans text-sm sm:text-base lg:columns-2 lg:gap-8"
          >
            Let's cut to the chase, this isn't a rags to riches story. I am just
            a teenager who wants to make a difference.<br /><br />
            I started out programming in Scratch, and eventually moved on to other
            languages and finally landed on TypeScript. I have been in love with
            building cool and weird stuff ever since.<br /><br />
            The internet opened me up to an insane number of opportunities and ideas
            but while the world is lost in hype, I care about the small things -
            the visuals that tell a story, interfaces that are intuitive, and systems
            that <i>just work</i>.<br /><br />
            My mission is to change the world or at least try to because why not?
            Oh and for some context, I'm from Calcutta, IN and a high school student.<br
            /><br />
            If I was able to intrigue you, here's a list of <a
              href="/everything"
              class="text-green-500 underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors duration-300 ease-in-out hover:text-green-600"
              >everything I've ever built, tried, thought of, or failed at</a
            >.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="-mx-4 mt-12 border-t border-black sm:-mx-8 sm:mt-16 md:-mx-16 md:mt-20 lg:-mx-24 lg:mt-24"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 px-4 py-4 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24"
        >
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-4 font-ellograph text-sm font-semibold sm:gap-6 sm:text-base"
          >
            <a href="https://x.com/py_bash1">Twitter</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/pybash1">GitHub</a>
          </div>
          <div class="font-ellograph text-sm font-semibold sm:text-base">
            &copy; 2025, PyBash
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
